            <title>DeepSeek AI 技術成關鍵   82 歲高齡患者成功完成腎盂癌根治手術</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/23/deepseek-ai/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=deepseek-ai</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/23/deepseek-ai/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 23 Feb 2025 06:21:02 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[健康]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[DeepSeek]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293587</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>四川省人民醫院泌尿外科成功為一名 82 歲高齡患者王爺爺（化名）完成了一項極具挑戰的根治性手術。患者原本因腎盂癌合併下腔靜脈癌栓，身體狀況不佳而未能進行手術。然而，憑藉最新的人工智能技術 DeepSeek 系統與虛擬三維重建技術的應用，手術順利進行，術後康復情況良好，王爺爺即將出院。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293597" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nimg2ws126net-1-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nimg2ws126net-1-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nimg2ws126net-1.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: #262626; min-height: 19px;"><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Songti TC'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: #262626;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">王爺爺在一個多月前被診斷為「右側腎盂癌伴下腔靜脈癌栓」，但由於年事已高且伴有心肺功能問題，當時醫療團隊並未急於施行手術。隨著病情惡化，癌栓阻塞下腔靜脈，導致雙下肢水腫並引發劇烈腰痛，患者常需依賴止痛藥才能入睡，且隨時有可能因癌栓脫落引發肺栓塞。情況危急，王爺爺於</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;"> 2 </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">月</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;"> 2 </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">日決定求診四川省人民醫院泌尿外科，並接受了專業團隊的全面評估。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: #262626; min-height: 19px;"><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Songti TC'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: #262626;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">雖然腎盂癌合併下腔靜脈癌栓手術難度極高，且王爺爺的高齡和身體狀況為手術增添了諸多風險，醫生團隊依然決定利用現代科技破局。四川省人民醫院泌尿外科主任熊瑋表示，這項手術的成功，離不開</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;"> DeepSeek </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">系統和三維重建技術的支援。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Songti TC'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: #262626;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">DeepSeek </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">通過對大量高齡患者的手術數據進行深度學習，迅速進行手術前、手術中和手術後的風險預警，幫助團隊設計用藥方案和康復路徑，還能根據患者的具體情況動態調整抗凝方案，極大降低了術後急性腎損傷的風險。術後僅兩天，王爺爺的血清肌酐水平便恢復正常，顯示了此係統在術後康復管理中的強大效能。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: #262626; min-height: 19px;"><span style="font-kerning: none;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293602" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nimgws126net-2-433x580.jpeg" alt="" width="433" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nimgws126net-2-433x580.jpeg 433w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nimgws126net-2.jpeg 673w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 433px" /></span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293601" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nimg1ws126net-1.jpeg" alt="" width="303" height="540" /></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Songti TC'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: #262626;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">另一方面，三維重建技術提供了精確的手術預演，通過毫米級的空間定位，清楚地呈現癌栓與周邊血管的關係，並模擬最佳的血管控制路徑。這使得手術團隊可以在術前設計多套方案，並在手術中選擇最優方案，顯著縮短了決策時間。最終手術過程順利，手術團隊只用 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">49 </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">分鐘便成功完成下腔靜脈的重建和重新開通。手術後，王爺爺並未進入重症監護室，而是直接回到了病房進行康復治療。經過充分的恢復，他的腎功能已恢復正常，並且雙下肢水腫已完全消失，即將順利出院。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: #262626; min-height: 19px;"><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Songti TC'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: #262626;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">熊瑋指手術成功證明 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">AI </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">技術的應用能夠有效提升醫療團隊的能力，還展示瞭如何將外科醫生的經驗轉化為智能資產，降低手術風險，強化醫患共同體。他認為，未來這一技術模式將有望形成「</span><span style="font-kerning: none; color: #1d1d1d;">高齡腫瘤患者智慧診療管理模式</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">」，推動醫療行業從依賴傳統經驗向數據驅動的智能化轉型。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: #262626; min-height: 19px;"><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Songti TC'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: #262626;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">對於人工智能是否會取代醫生的工作，熊瑋並不擔心。他強調，科技的進步主要是幫助醫生解決「能不能做」的問題，而非替代醫生。新的技術讓醫生能夠更專注於「是否該做」的價值判斷，並且有助於醫生在手術過程中發揮必要的勇氣、智慧和臨牀判斷力，這些是目前</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">AI</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">無法替代的核心能力。</span></p><p data-start="997" data-end="1128"><p data-start="997" data-end="1128"><p data-start="997" data-end="1128">資料來源：<a href="https://www.163.com/dy/article/JOU8BEF30514R9MQ.html">錦觀新聞</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
